---
title: Pork Sausages & Parmesan Mash with Caramelised Onion & Garlic Veggies
description: This is a classic meal but not like you know it! The pork sausages are packed with homestyle flavour and the mash is upgraded with Parmesan cheese and chives. With caramelised onion topping it off, dinner comes together with a bang!
